'''Mine-sniffer droids''' were droids specialized for finding [[Mine/Legends|mines]]. Some mine-sniffers were stoned to destruction by the [[Red Knights of Life]] in the [[Square of Hopeful Redemption]] on [[Rhommamool/Legends|Rhommamool]].

